# Code Victorian — required environment variables
# Copy to .env.local for local dev and set in Vercel for deployments.
# See STRIPE_SETUP.md for full Stripe Dashboard setup steps.

# ----- Stripe (required for /donate) ---------------------------------
# Test mode while you're verifying the integration; switch to sk_live_…
# only when you're ready to take real money.
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_replace_me
# From Stripe Dashboard → Developers → Webhooks → your endpoint →
# "Signing secret". A new whsec_… is issued per endpoint, so test mode
# and live mode have different values.
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_replace_me

# ----- Optional ------------------------------------------------------
# Override the origin used in Stripe success/cancel redirects.
# Defaults to the request Origin header, then https://<VERCEL_URL>,
# then https://code-victorian.vercel.app.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_ORIGIN=https://codevictorian.com

# ----- Petition / Campaign Nucleus -----------------------------------
# Override the CN form receiver URL (defaults to the published one in
# app/api/petition/route.ts).
# CN_PETITION_RECEIVER_URL=https://teller.campaignnucleus.com/forms/receiver/…

# ----- 21st-dev ChatWidget (only needed if you re-enable the widget) -
# API_KEY_21ST=…
